collections.name: Chill Pixels
collections.description:
Unleash the cool vibes with Chill Pixels, a pixel-art penguin that’s as stylish as it is unique! This retro-inspired digital artwork features a bold black-and-white penguin rocking a red scarf, a bright blue bandana, and a confident stance that exudes charisma. Set against a vibrant color-blocked background, this NFT embodies the spirit of adventure, fun, and pixel-perfect nostalgia.

Perfect for collectors who appreciate pixel art, digital nostalgia, and quirky characters, Chill Pixels is more than just an NFT—it’s a statement! Own this piece and bring a little more chill to your collection. 🐧🎨

collections.name: TheTruth
collections.description:
Do we have the right to know the truth?

This NFT project is a grand experiment in creating a new model of historical compilation. As a fully on-chain initiative, it records all daily events and socially significant news directly onto the blockchain, enabling tamper-proof ownership that can be passed on to future generations. As this “on-chain history” accumulates, it remains resilient in the face of political or economic pressures, preserving its truth and steadily growing in cultural and academic value over the long term.NFT metadata is recorded on the Symbol blockchain.

collections.name: Soundscape Avatar Accessory Closet
collections.description: The Soundscape Avatar Accessory Closet is the soulbound collection of locked apparel and accessories for SAN Soundscape Avatars, created for those ready to commit to their ultimate on-chain identity. Each trait permanently enhances an avatar's volume and frequency scores, solidifying its individuality and performance. When a Soundscape Avatar Accessory Marketplace trait is applied to an avatar, it transforms into a SANBOUND token—permanently tied to the avatar's identity. Beyond style, these traits unlock digital and physical rewards through the Soundscape App, including premium audio experiences, events, and exclusive collectibles.

collections.name: Gods of the Sky
collections.description:
Goods of the Sky" is a digital collection that blends mythological figures with modern art, exploring divine entities and their universal attributes through the lens of digital creativity. This collection delves into power, beauty, passion, and justice, transcending time and space, creating a deep connection between mythological characters and contemporary art.

Each NFT in the collection is not only a tribute to the gods of the sky but also a reinterpretation of their emotional and symbolic depths through digital artistry. Every creation within Goods of the Sky invites reflection on the balance of power, beauty, and creation, as well as the eternal impact these deities have on human culture and art.

collections.name: The Emoji Project
collections.description:
These NFTs are part of The Emoji Project—a set of uniquely designed, Web3-native emoji expressions that go beyond traditional emojis. Inspired by the open-source creativity of OpenMoji, this collection builds upon and reimagines digital expression for the decentralized era. 

Each NFT is a fully unique, collectible reaction icon that represents a mood, meme, or moment in the metaverse.Whether used as a collectible, a digital identity marker, or a piece of art, this NFT represents a new way to express yourself in Web3—bridging the past, present, and future of emoji culture.
